{"tid":58620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣人：我們都是說「普通話」，但文言文很糟！","createTime":"2016-12-29T03:25:04.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-29T07:11:27.000Z","uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ab26ad8a1823066f62e82a3b45c0f3825fe58742","tid":58620,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T03:25:04.000Z","msg":"日前有人在「粵語（廣東話）社團」群組，上載一張聲稱攝自將軍澳某商場的相片，從畫面可見，一間疑似補習社的玻璃門上，貼有「你能聽懂普通話，就能學好文言文」句子，相片隨即被網民瘋傳，不少人抨擊該補習社，有人更留言直斥這種說法「誤人子弟」，認為應學好繁體字和粵語，才可學好中國各地方言和文章，「文言文嗰陣都未有普通話，真係九唔搭八！」<br />\n<br />\n該群組成員來自不同地區，帖文者上載相片時，補上一句「正仆街，香港都變成噉？」有網民留言指「好想知此等『人之患』師承何師何校」、「普通話是文言文嗎？有病！」有人亦提到曾鈺成曾在專欄中，以李清照名句「悽悽慘慘戚戚」舉例，指普通話的「戚」字，不但由入聲變成平聲，而且讀音和「悽」一樣，於是讀起來變成「悽悽慘慘悽悽」，令原有味道全失。<br />\n<br />\n有台灣人亦留言，指該說法沒有根據，「叫他少在那邊誤人子弟，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我從小就是講普通話（台灣人，其實我們叫國語）我文言文一樣很糟啊！</span></span>」有網民直言，普通話才是「毀滅文言文」的元兇。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20161228/19879312\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20161228%2F19879312&d=CLTC44eENDWC4%2FMg%2FfkLu0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=da731a84\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20161228%2F19879312&h=95aef006\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20161228/19879312</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">話國語唔係普通話既出一出來</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d28a8eb0bd4d47d8bff50ae7a53dd4d0ea1a1ae6","tid":58620,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T03:27:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXyEakqP4M2uUCN7NvgwkyLZgupyK6WZP5xLT1v3Djptv?filename=Zv88s4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZv88s4.jpg&h=b23d149b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n叫法唔同就變左第二樣野？"},{"pid":"8bf520bbce773af010cd7291169359afe075a1b8","tid":58620,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T03:34:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXyEakqP4M2uUCN7NvgwkyLZgupyK6WZP5xLT1v3Djptv?filename=Zv88s4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZv88s4.jpg&h=b23d149b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n叫法唔同就變左第二樣野？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大陸人先會叫普通話"},{"pid":"829b555f8155da5ff63be084ac4979e62febf1fd","tid":58620,"uid":59626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T04:37:56.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"4ac3359a58e5c9ce9a8dcef313b8156cf015702c","tid":58620,"uid":1295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T04:53:06.000Z","msg":"普通話由北方語音為基礎整出黎，一切用中共標準，跟台灣的國語只可以話相近但唔可以話一樣，至少併音已經唔一樣"},{"pid":"0e25e0933ca5784163fd4d3ac6e875d37e793ce4","tid":58620,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T05:08:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>普通話由北方語音為基礎整出黎，一切用中共標準，跟台灣的國語只可以話相近但唔可以話一樣，至少併音已經唔一樣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大同小異，等於英式英文同美式英文"},{"pid":"6ddc7b35e06b03c1a7294c3597abf1a24fa42ff8","tid":58620,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T05:34:05.000Z","msg":"用胡語讀《燕詩》，兒化調搞到不倫不類 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e02e2f6dd6fac3129c39c2a2af475a15a340a502","tid":58620,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T05:37:19.000Z","msg":"同一樣野講幾百次你煩唔煩，撚屌五毛<br />\n<br />\n香港就係講廣東話，就係咁簡單<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/29/133630_85b0847e7eb808a433c5b8234e93681a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F29%2F133630_85b0847e7eb808a433c5b8234e93681a.jpg&h=24acd0b6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dbe6b377ce124956612c102c70f1e75b5a89ede7","tid":58620,"uid":54411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T07:06:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>普通話由北方語音為基礎整出黎，一切用中共標準，跟台灣的國語只可以話相近但唔可以話一樣，至少併音已經唔一樣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大同小異，等於英式英文同美式英文</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n9成5一樣。<br />\n但有班人成日話 兩者唔同，咩心態？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68e198bb23e2adbe738ad8a5e14dc1780bdd7a97","tid":58620,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T07:11:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同一樣野講幾百次你煩唔煩，撚屌五毛<br />\n<br />\n香港就係講廣東話，就係咁簡單<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/29/133630_85b0847e7eb808a433c5b8234e93681a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F29%2F133630_85b0847e7eb808a433c5b8234e93681a.jpg&h=24acd0b6&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪撚理佢啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}